title: Alexandra Road Estate
description: Stepped ziggurat housing terraces with south-facing balconies; a landmark in low-rise, high-density design.

body.raw:
## Architectural notes

Careful section provides generous sunlight and privacy; pedestrian streets form the estate's spine.
